<h1 class="nhsuk-heading-xl">Tender</h1>

<p class="nhsuk-lead-paragraph">
  The Observatory will appoint a digital delivery partner to build the production service. This page
  will host the invitation to tender and how to express interest.
</p>

<h2 class="nhsuk-heading-l">What we are looking for</h2>
<ul class="nhsuk-list nhsuk-list--bullet">
  <li>A partner experienced in user-centred, accessible public-service delivery (in the spirit of the GOV.UK and NHS service standards).</li>
  <li>Mainstream, modern approaches to digital delivery that work well outside the NHS, applied at pace.</li>
  <li>Genuine co-production with patients, families and clinical specialists in haematology and emergency care.</li>
  <li>Working in the open, with open-source outputs.</li>
</ul>

<h2 class="nhsuk-heading-l">Scope</h2>
<p class="nhsuk-body">
  A production service for personalised sickle cell care plans, accessible to sickle cell services,
  patients and medics in acute settings — including NHS Care Identity (CIS2) sign-in, assured
  information governance, NHS-approved hosting, and clinical safety assurance. A working prototype
  and full requirements are available in the project repository.
</p>

<div class="nhsuk-inset-text">
  <p>Interested in delivering this? See <a class="nhsuk-link" href="{{ '/contact/' | url }}">Contact</a>.
  The prototype and requirements are in the <a class="nhsuk-link" href="{{ site.repoUrl }}">project repository</a>.</p>
</div>
